    <section class="section-top">
      <h1>YOUR ACHIEVEMENTS<span> UNLOCKED</span></h1>
      <p>
        Learn from the industry's best coaches at Gamer Guru, the world's
        premier
        <br />
        esports coaching platform. Start your journey and unlock your
        achievements.
      </p>
      <button><a href="/booking"> BOOK YOUR SESSION </a></button>
    </section>
    <section class="grid">
      <div class="column">
        <img src="images final/scout.png" alt="image1" />
        <h2>SKILLS <span>ASSESSMENT</span></h2>
        <p>Start your journey with a 30-minute evaluation of your gaming skills
          from an Expert Sensei and receive a personalized plan to improve.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="column">
        <img src="/images final/mortal.png" alt="image2" />
        <h2>ONE-ON-ONE <span>COACHING</span></h2>
        <p>Step into a live, one-on-one 60-minute training session designed to
          help you improve your personal skills in the specific genre and game
          of your choice.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="column">
        <img src="/images final/payal.png" alt="image3" />
        <h2>TEAM <span>SESSIONS</span></h2>
        <p>Squad up, dive deep into team tactics, and learn how to communicate,
          coordinate, and dominate on the virtual battlefield from a certified
          Sensei.</p>
      </div>
    </section>
    <hr class="grid-hr" />
    <!-- This section is for  cards and dropdown button (start) -->
    <div class="drop_down_back">
      <div id="DROP_DOWN">
        <span class="custom-dropdown big">
          <h3 class="step"> Step 1</h3>
          <select
            class="dropmenu"
            name="slct1"
            id="slct1"
            onchange="populate(this.id, 'slct2')"
          >
            <div>
              <option value=""> CHOOSE THE GAME</option>
              <option value="FORTNITE">FORTNITE</option>
              <option value="LEAGUE OF LEGENDS">LEAGUE OF LEGENDS</option>
              <option>DOTA 2</option>
