        success on the world stage. Each Guru is vetted using a proprietary
        process to meet our world-class standard and onboarded by a renowned
        esports psychologist, ensuring universal quality care and support across
        our vast network of trainers and services.They know the games, the maps,
        the mechanics, and the secrets to success.</p>
